"animal" includes cattle, horses, sheep, goats and pigs;
"cattle" means any bull, cow, ox, steer, heifer or calf;
"declared area" means any portion of Zambia to which the provisions of this Act
have been declared to apply;
"flock" means any number of sheep or goats, more than one, which are in one lot,
or under the charge of one person;
"goat" means any ram, ewe, wether or kid;
